```powershell
.\configure_claude.ps1
```
*(Pass `-BaseUrl http://your-api-host:PORT` if needed)*

The script will:
1. Create a `.venv` virtual environment and install dependencies
2. Write a `{{ project_slug }}` entry into your Claude Desktop config
3. Tell you to restart Claude Desktop

